model. How do you, you know, what are the security risks? Are people going to train on my data? I

00:37:45.479 --> 00:37:50.280
think engaging the right stakeholders on the IT security side has got to be a big part of it.

00:37:50.439 --> 00:37:54.360
On the IT security side has gotten me a lot of wins and buy-ins, because it feels like

00:37:54.360 --> 00:37:58.600
