many things you could do. And what if I add this data set? And what if I add that? It is a,

00:40:56.679 --> 00:41:03.239
you have a career, you know, and take advantage that you have time to get to where you want to

00:41:03.239 --> 00:41:07.800
go. And there will be bumps along the way. There have been absolutely bumps along the way,

